- Board ID: `4`.
- Board API name: `HFT board`; board location is `Hatyai-flood-Tracker (HFT)`.
- Board type is `simple`, so it does not support sprints.

Keep early implementation simple with `frontend/`, `backend/`, and `docs/` directories. Prefer mock data with stable API-shaped contracts before integrating fragile external data sources.

